'''越野拉力賽'''（{{lang-en|Rally raid, cross-country rallying}}）是超長距離的{{tsl|en|Off-road racing|汽車越野賽|汽車越野競賽}}，參賽者可能要連續3至15天比賽，總賽程可達600至5,000公里，途經的地方可以包括沙丘、林道、山路和乾涸的河床等等<ref name="fiaccregs">{{cite web|url=https://www.fia.com/file/75699/download/16519|format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]]|title=FIA Cross-Country Rallies General Prescriptions – 2019|work=fia.com|date=10 December 2018|access-date=15 March 2019}}</ref><ref name="fimccregs">{{cite web|url=http://www.fim-live.com/en/library/download/73928/no_cache/1/|format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]]|title= 2019 FIM Cross-Country Rallies World Championship Regulations |work=fim-live.com|date=13 February 2019|access-date=15 March 2019}}</ref><ref name="fimbajaregs">{{cite web|url=http://www.fim-live.com/en/library/download/73926/no_cache/1/|format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]]|title= 2019 FIM Bajas World Cup Regulations |work=fim-live.com|date=12 February 2019|access-date=15 March 2019}}</ref>。

著名的越野拉力賽是[[達喀爾拉力賽|達喀爾拉力賽]]，參賽車種包括汽車、卡車和摩托車，Roadbook、[[地圖|地圖]]和[[GPS|GPS]]是參賽者必要的裝備。

